Docker Advantages
- Packages everything 
- If it runs on dev machine can run on any other machine with docker

When dockerized 
- Packs all dependecies
- Packs all enviroment varibles
- Cut-down OS included
- A runtime enviroment included
- Application files included

Container : Isolated enviroment for running apps

How are containers different from virtual machines?
VM are physical machine.  Like mac use hypervisor for creating different vms.VM is resource intensive. Containers also give isolatation but less resource intensive and can run on any host . Starts quickly.

Docker Architecture:

Client-Server architechture . Client reaches docker engine using restful API. 